# Dependencies & build artifacts (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
.turbo

# Env files — secrets are injected at runtime via docker-compose, never baked in
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Local / editor / VCS
.git
.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*

# NOTE: apps/mobile and apps/device-simulator are intentionally NOT ignored —
# npm workspaces / npm ci require every workspace package.json declared in
# package-lock.json to be present in the build context.

# Docker files themselves
Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
docker/
DOCKER.md
